#### PR description:

* Remove obsolete class GEMVfatStatusDigi
* Remove obsolete collections
  * GEMAMCdataCollection
  * GEMAMC13EventCollection
  * GEMGEBdataCollection
  * GEMVfatStatusDigiCollection
* remove gem namespace
* change to better class name 
  * AMC13Event  GEMAMC13
  * AMCdata  GEMAMC
  * GEBdata  GEMOptoHybrid
  * VFATdata  GEMVFAT
* no changes to functionalities 
* [presented](https://indico.cern.ch/event/1065674/contributions/4480945/attachments/2292860/3898709/gem_unpacker_20210810.pdf) at GEM DPG meeting

Validated with wf 11634.0 and 34611.0
